       two non empty non-overlapping open sets.  (Contributed by FL,
       17-Nov-2008.) $)
    usinuniop $p |- ( J e. Con -> A. x e. J A. y e. J
       ( ( x =/= (/) /\ y =/= (/) /\ ( x i^i y ) = (/) )
         -> X =/= ( x u. y ) ) ) $=
      ( wcel c0 wne wceq wi wa wn wo wal wb impcom sylibr sylbir ex sylbi eleq1
